Description
-------------

This is a program that efficiently parses text input from a large file.
It will display a count of a provided word as well as a list of the line numbers
it occurs on.

Usage
-------------
This program requires only standard c libraries and an included dbg.h file.
It can be built by compiling with the make command.

make textFileSearch

./textFileSearch <filename>

to search any .txt file

or

./textFileSearch -h

to see options and more info on how to search.
